OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,FPlans to build a new 5,500 seater Kop
OL,7,Fstand at Wrexham AFC's Racecourse
OL,8,FGround have been given the green light
OL,9,Fby a planning committee.
OL,11,FWrexham County Borough councillors
OL,12,Fapproved the scheme for SToK Cae Ras
OL,13,Fon Monday night.
OL,15,FIt comes one month after the proposals
OL,16,Fwere unveiled by the club's CEO
OL,17,FMichael Williamson, who said it was
OL,18,Fpart of a plan to restore the
OL,19,Ftraditional four-sided enclosure of
OL,20,Fthe stadium.
