OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,FThe idea for the new stand is to
OL,7,Fcreate a home end for Wrexham fans
OL,8,F"that will reinforce the atmosphere",
OL,9,Fwith design of the roof "optimised to
OL,10,Famplify sound from the spectators
OL,11,Ftowards the pitch," he said.
OL,13,FThere were no formal objections to the
OL,14,Fplans, despite concerns raised by
OL,15,FWrexham University that the
OL,16,Fdevelopment would make its original
OL,17,Fplans to create a student village at
OL,18,FCrispin Lane impossible to deliver.
