OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,FWrexham AFC CEO Mr Williamson told the
OL,7,Fcommittee: "When Rob McElhenney and
OL,8,FRyan Reynolds became co-chairmen four
OL,9,Fyears ago, one of their core aims was
OL,10,Fto recreate a four-sided stadium.
OL,12,F"An early brief for a replacement Kop
OL,13,Fstrand was approved in 2022, but our
OL,14,Famazing success on and off the pitch
OL,15,Fover the last few seasons required a
OL,16,Freview of our ambition for the SToK
OL,17,FCae Ras...
