OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,F"We want to create a unique and
OL,7,Finstantly recognisable Kop stand with
OL,8,Fits brick design and form that
OL,9,Frepresents the city's identity."
OL,11,FMr Williamson told the committee that
OL,12,Fthe new Kop stand would be able to
OL,13,Faccommodate more fans than the 5,500
OL,14,Fseats they were currently seeking,
OL,15,Fthereby "future-proofing" the stadium
OL,16,F` though he added that any additional
OL,17,Fcapacity would require a new planning
OL,18,Fapplication.
