OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,FThe Racecourse Ground will host the
OL,7,FUEFA Euro U19s tournament to be held
OL,8,Facross North Wales in summer 2026.
OL,10,FAccording to design plans, the new Kop
OL,11,FStand will accommodate both safe
OL,12,Fstanding areas and accessible seating.
OL,14,FThe stand will also feature
OL,15,Fhospitality areas and will double as
OL,16,Fthe entrance to the pitch for players
OL,17,Fand officials.
