OL,3,CPlans for new 5,500 seater Kop stand
OL,4,Cgiven green light
OL,6,FCllr Phil Wynn, whose ward
OL,7,FBrynyffynnon is next to the
OL,8,FRacecourse, welcomed the plans but
OL,9,Fsaid there would need to be further
OL,10,Fconsultation around matchday traffic
OL,11,Fshould the club look to expand further.
OL,13,FHe said: "I very much welcome this
OL,14,Frevised application. It will be easier
OL,15,Fon the eye especially for residents
OL,16,Fwho live within the view of the stand.
