OL,6,F"I do welcome petition 15 which is the
OL,7,Frequirement of the club to submit and
OL,8,Fthe council to approve a travel plan.
OL,9,FUltimately those 400 householders in
OL,10,Fmy ward who live next to the ground
OL,11,Fare concerned about the impact on
OL,12,Ftheir lives on matchday.
OL,14,F"If the capacity does increase in
OL,15,Ffuture I would welcome discussion with
OL,16,Fthe club about how we address the
OL,17,Fconcerns around matchday parking at
OL,18,Fthat point."
