OL,6,FCllr David Bithell, whose Stansty ward
OL,7,Falso neighbours the ground, also
OL,8,Fwelcomed the plans.
OL,10,F"I welcome and support this
OL,11,Fapplication," he said.
OL,13,F"The Racecourse is a key site in the
OL,14,Femerging Wrexham Gateway regeneration
OL,15,Fproject and it's going to enhance the
OL,16,Farea. It's all good news for Wrexham
OL,17,FCity Centre and the town."
